    <item>
      <title>信贷如此火爆，交易员纷纷做空</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-23/credit-s-so-hot-that-traders-are-building-shorts-credit-weekly</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于全球经济保持强劲，有钱可花、新交易很少的资产管理公司已将信贷利差推至接近历史最低水平。这对一些人来说是一个信号，表明是时候购买下行保护了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-23/credit-s-so-hot-that-traders-are-building-shorts-credit-weekly</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 23 Nov 2024 19:41:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度太阳能机构确认阿达尼起诉书的关键细节</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-23/key-detail-in-adani-indictment-confirmed-by-indian-solar-agency</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度负责拍卖阿达尼绿色能源有限公司 (Adani Green Energy Ltd.) 起诉案中的太阳能项目的机构证实，在最初的中标者拒绝开发后，该机构已将 2.3 千兆瓦的容量分配给了该企业集团。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-23/key-detail-in-adani-indictment-confirmed-by-indian-solar-agency</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 23 Nov 2024 18:36:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>维勒鲁瓦称欧洲央行可以独立于美联储举措降低利率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-23/ecb-can-lower-rates-independent-of-fed-moves-villeroy-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会委员弗朗索瓦·维勒鲁瓦·德加洛表示，无论美联储发生什么，欧洲央行的政策都会继续发展。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-23/ecb-can-lower-rates-independent-of-fed-moves-villeroy-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 23 Nov 2024 18:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>对于押注股市上涨的华尔街专业人士来说，历史毫无用处</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-23/history-is-useless-for-wall-street-pros-betting-on-stocks-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[投资者在押注总统大选后通常会出现的股市反弹时面临着一个挑战：由于标准普尔 500 指数有望创下今年以来的最佳开局之一，因此这次不能以历史为鉴。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-23/history-is-useless-for-wall-street-pros-betting-on-stocks-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 23 Nov 2024 14:00:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥斥资 27 亿美元扩建港口，无视特朗普威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-23/mexico-looks-past-trump-trade-threat-with-2-7-billion-manzanillo-port-expansion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥并不担心即将上任的特朗普政府的关税威胁，无论其北方邻国和最大贸易伙伴采取什么行动，它都看好全球商品贸易的光明未来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-23/mexico-looks-past-trump-trade-threat-with-2-7-billion-manzanillo-port-expansion</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 23 Nov 2024 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>迪拜房地产热潮让买家想方设法抢占地盘</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-23/dubai-real-estate-boom-investors-eying-reits-fractional-ownership-apps</link>
      <description><![CDATA[迪拜已逐渐成为全球最热门的房地产市场之一，但其房价却越来越高，买家也因此对房地产投资信托的兴趣再度燃起，许多人开始转向分期付款仅需 136 美元的房地产部分所有权应用程序。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-23/dubai-real-estate-boom-investors-eying-reits-fractional-ownership-apps</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 23 Nov 2024 13:29:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比特币跌破 10 万美元，大目标在望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/bitcoin-btc-flirts-with-100-000-on-optimism-over-us-crypto-outlook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[截至目前，周末比特币的交易价格仍远低于 10 万美元的里程碑价位，这再一次粉碎了爱好者们对这一最古老的数字资产将突破这一重要财务和心理门槛的希望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/bitcoin-btc-flirts-with-100-000-on-optimism-over-us-crypto-outlook</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 23:18:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
